{
  "$schema_note": "Hand-maintained legacy URL map for Cloudflare cutover. Solo editor: add a row whenever you rename or retire a path. See docs/LEGACY_URLS.md.",
  "version": 1,
  "status": 301,
  "canonicalExtension": ".html",
  "notes": [
    "Targets use .html to match files on disk today. When clean (extensionless) URLs ship, strip .html from 'to' (or generate at deploy).",
